240
00:17:19,288 --> 00:17:21,206
Nanti pak cik buang, jangan risau.

241
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:23,167
Pak cik biarkan saja.

242
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:24,668
Susah nak alihkan semua ini.

243
00:17:25,669 --> 00:17:26,962
Kita kitar semula.

244
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:33,218
Dulu ini tempat apa?

245
00:17:34,344 --> 00:17:35,888
- Restoran Cina?
- Apa?

246
00:17:35,971 --> 00:17:38,724
Aduh, apa namanya?

247
00:17:39,266 --> 00:17:41,685
Mereka ramalkan masa depan…

248
00:17:42,728 --> 00:17:44,521
AI? Data raya?

249
00:17:44,605 --> 00:17:45,439
Apa?

250
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:49,234
Ya, pak cik rasa begitulah.

251
00:17:52,237 --> 00:17:55,115
Pak cik tak rasa ada bau pelik?

252
00:17:56,158 --> 00:17:57,743
Itu bau kertas dinding.

253
00:17:57,826 --> 00:17:59,578
Nanti hilanglah. Jangan risau.

254
00:18:01,455 --> 00:18:04,458
Tiada tempat begini di sini.

255
00:18:04,541 --> 00:18:06,919
Tuhan dah banyak tolong kamu.

256
00:18:07,002 --> 00:18:08,712
Tipu hantu bolehlah, bukan saya.

257
00:18:08,796 --> 00:18:10,714
Sekarang ada banyak pejabat kosong.

258
00:18:12,674 --> 00:18:14,468
Sekejap, I-rang.

259
00:18:14,551 --> 00:18:15,969
Kamu nak ada pemandangan?

260
00:18:16,637 --> 00:18:17,471
Ikut pak cik.

261
00:18:24,269 --> 00:18:25,395
Cantik, bukan?

262
00:18:26,313 --> 00:18:27,481
Indah pemandangannya.

263
00:18:58,387 --> 00:19:01,765
Tak ada tempat lain dengan pemandangan
mahkamah begini dengan bajet kamu.

264
00:19:01,849 --> 00:19:03,433
Fikir masak-masak.

265
00:19:05,477 --> 00:19:06,687
Saya nak sewa.

266
00:19:06,770 --> 00:19:07,813
Saya suka.

267
00:19:13,235 --> 00:19:15,487
Macam itulah.

268
00:19:17,656 --> 00:19:19,408
Yahu.

269
00:19:24,413 --> 00:19:27,291
Saya nak papan tanda di atas sekali,

270
00:19:27,374 --> 00:19:29,084
sampai boleh nampak dari mahkamah.

271
00:19:32,754 --> 00:19:35,257
{\an8}FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG

272
00:19:45,309 --> 00:19:49,855
FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG

273
00:19:49,938 --> 00:19:52,232
PEGUAM SHIN I-RANG

274
00:19:52,316 --> 00:19:55,652
Memang keturunan aku pandai berniaga.

275
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:07,581
Itu bunyi apa?

276
00:20:15,672 --> 00:20:16,840
Apa ini?

277
00:20:34,191 --> 00:20:35,192
Kemenyan?

278
00:20:37,236 --> 00:20:39,571
Baguslah. Terasa pengap di sini.

279
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,085
Sedap.

280
00:21:27,035 --> 00:21:27,953
Apa?

281
00:21:28,996 --> 00:21:29,913
Mimpi saja?

282
00:21:35,919 --> 00:21:36,753
Hai.

283
00:21:36,837 --> 00:21:39,506
Hai, I-rang.
Ingat tak lelaki yang aku cakap dulu?

284
00:21:39,589 --> 00:21:40,507
Lelaki?

285
00:21:41,049 --> 00:21:42,009
Siapa?

286
00:21:42,092 --> 00:21:44,303
<i>Hari itu kau cakap nak jumpa paralegal.</i>

287
00:21:44,386 --> 00:21:46,096
Dia dah sampai.

288
00:21:46,179 --> 00:21:47,764
Nanti aku telefon balik.

289
00:21:47,848 --> 00:21:49,266
Apa? Helo?

290
00:21:50,183 --> 00:21:52,811
Bukan, orang dah upah dia.
Sebab itu aku telefon.

291
00:21:52,894 --> 00:21:54,229
Siapa yang datang?

292
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,481
Awal encik datang.

293
00:21:57,482 --> 00:21:58,567
Mesti encik tunggu lama.

294
00:21:58,650 --> 00:22:00,652
Biasanya saya bangun awal,

295
00:22:00,736 --> 00:22:02,487
tapi saya sibuk sikit kebelakangan ini.

296
00:22:04,531 --> 00:22:05,907
Encik boleh nampak saya?

297
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:07,701
Apa?

298
00:22:07,784 --> 00:22:09,745
Mestilah, sebab itu saya tegur encik.

299
00:22:15,834 --> 00:22:18,962
Saya pun tinggi,

300
00:22:19,046 --> 00:22:20,505
tapi taklah setinggi encik.

301
00:22:21,840 --> 00:22:22,883
Tinggi encik 190 cm?

302
00:22:22,966 --> 00:22:24,301
Mungkin 2 m?

303
00:22:41,735 --> 00:22:42,736
Encik…

304
00:22:42,819 --> 00:22:44,488
Kenapa?

305
00:22:44,571 --> 00:22:46,239
Hantu…

306
00:22:51,328 --> 00:22:52,162
Hantu!

307
00:22:52,245 --> 00:22:53,872
- Ada hantu!
- Alamak.

308
00:22:57,542 --> 00:22:59,836
Tuhan, Jesus Christ, Virgin Mary,
maafkan aku.

309
00:23:00,337 --> 00:23:03,090
Aku janji akan bayar deposit mak
dan ubah hidup aku.

310
00:23:03,173 --> 00:23:05,008
Jangan biarkan aku mati.

311
00:23:06,009 --> 00:23:07,135
Encik buat apa?

312
00:23:07,219 --> 00:23:08,595
Nak main sorok-sorok?

313
00:23:10,722 --> 00:23:12,474
Aduh. Mesti sakit.

314
00:23:14,017 --> 00:23:16,770
Pergi! Berambus!

315
00:23:16,853 --> 00:23:17,729
Pergi…

316
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:01,356
AI?

317
00:24:01,439 --> 00:24:02,816
Data raya?

318
00:24:04,568 --> 00:24:05,902
Dia tipu aku.

319
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,199
Macam-macam.

320
00:24:13,201 --> 00:24:14,411
Dengar sini.

321
00:24:14,995 --> 00:24:17,414
Hantu dah tak wujud pada zaman moden ini.

322
00:24:17,497 --> 00:24:19,541
Mesti ada bomoh seru dia.

323
00:24:19,624 --> 00:24:21,001
Bomoh apa?

324
00:24:23,003 --> 00:24:25,255
Nah, tengok.

325
00:24:26,006 --> 00:24:27,841
Ini buktinya.

326
00:24:28,383 --> 00:24:31,094
Pak cik tak cakap siapa pemilik lama.
Batalkan sekarang.

327
00:24:31,178 --> 00:24:32,637
Menurut undang-undang hartanah,

328
00:24:32,721 --> 00:24:36,683
pak cik tak perlu beritahu kamu
siapa pemilik sebelum ini.

329
00:24:38,768 --> 00:24:39,769
Ada lagi.

330
00:24:40,270 --> 00:24:42,480
Menurut Artikel Empat,
Perenggan Lima kontrak,

331
00:24:42,564 --> 00:24:45,525
"Penyewa boleh batalkan kontrak

332
00:24:45,609 --> 00:24:48,028
jika tak dimaklumkan
sebarang keadaan tak diingini."

333
00:24:48,111 --> 00:24:50,822
Tak ada orang inginkan pejabat berhantu.

334
00:24:51,823 --> 00:24:53,408
Nak ikut undang-undang pula?

335
00:24:53,491 --> 00:24:56,286
Okey, buktikan yang ada hantu di sini.

336
00:24:56,369 --> 00:24:57,329
Aduh.

337
00:25:00,123 --> 00:25:01,791
Itu dia. Dia ada di sini.

338
00:25:01,875 --> 00:25:02,876
Di sana.

339
00:25:02,959 --> 00:25:03,793
Mana?

340
00:25:05,378 --> 00:25:06,421
Itu!

341
00:25:06,504 --> 00:25:08,131
Itu. Itu dia!

342
00:25:08,215 --> 00:25:09,716
Mana?

343
00:25:09,799 --> 00:25:12,761
- Pak cik memang tak nampak dia?
- Nampak apa?

344
00:25:13,345 --> 00:25:14,930
Sudahlah, I-rang.

345
00:25:15,472 --> 00:25:16,431
Pelik-pelik saja.

346
00:25:16,514 --> 00:25:18,516
Susahnya cakap dengan dia!

347
00:25:22,437 --> 00:25:23,730
Mungkin ini puncanya.

348
00:25:23,813 --> 00:25:25,106
PEGUAM SHIN I-RANG

349
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:31,071
<i>Ada satu kisah bertajuk Legenda Arang.</i>

350
00:25:31,738 --> 00:25:33,949
<i>Setiap kali ada</i>
<i>majistret daerah baru dilantik,</i>

351
00:25:34,032 --> 00:25:36,576
<i>dia akan dikunjungi hantu dara yang marah.</i>

352
00:25:37,369 --> 00:25:40,705
<i>Hantu itu bunuh semua majistret lembik.</i>

353
00:25:46,836 --> 00:25:47,796
Rimasnya.

354
00:25:49,339 --> 00:25:50,674
Bangun.

355
00:25:50,757 --> 00:25:51,758
Ini mimpi saja.

356
00:25:54,970 --> 00:25:56,179
<i>Tapi,</i>

357
00:25:56,263 --> 00:25:59,015
<i>- ada seorang majistret berani terselamat…</i>
- Nanti dulu!

358
00:25:59,099 --> 00:26:01,726
<i>…dan tolong hantu itu</i>
<i>selesaikan perhitungannya</i>

359
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:05,146
<i>dalam kisah indah ini.</i>

360
00:26:07,190 --> 00:26:08,900
Indah konon.

361
00:26:10,402 --> 00:26:12,654
Tengok apa? Kau bukan hantu dara pun.

362
00:26:13,446 --> 00:26:14,322
Minta maaf.

363
00:26:15,490 --> 00:26:16,616
Dia bercakap.

364
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:19,411
Pak cik dengar tak? Dia bercakap tadi.

365
00:26:20,203 --> 00:26:21,788
Wah.

366
00:26:21,871 --> 00:26:24,082
Kamu memang pandai berlakon.

367
00:26:26,167 --> 00:26:28,253
Tak. Pak cik tak nak mengalah.

368
00:26:28,336 --> 00:26:29,170
Saya pun.

369
00:26:29,254 --> 00:26:31,965
Saya tak nak sewa pejabat ini.

370
00:26:32,048 --> 00:26:34,426
Kalau pak cik berkeras juga,
kita jumpa di mahkamah.

371
00:26:35,051 --> 00:26:36,594
Kalau begitu, apa boleh buat?

372
00:26:36,678 --> 00:26:38,346
Pak cik kena bincang dengan Pn. Park.

373
00:26:38,847 --> 00:26:40,473
Mesti dia baru tutup kedai.

374
00:26:40,557 --> 00:26:42,350
Harap-harap, dia tak letih.

375
00:26:42,434 --> 00:26:43,768
Sudah.

376
00:26:45,020 --> 00:26:47,981
Siapa kamu paling takut?
Hantu atau mak kamu?

377
00:27:01,119 --> 00:27:04,873
Pak cik beri kamu masa beberapa hari
sebelum bayar sewa, okey?

378
00:27:09,878 --> 00:27:11,379
Pak cik, tunggu!

379
00:27:16,926 --> 00:27:18,595
Kau kena pergi sebelum esok.

380
00:27:18,678 --> 00:27:19,804
Kalau tak,

381
00:27:19,888 --> 00:27:21,723
aku datang bawa salib dan Bible.

382
00:27:29,189 --> 00:27:32,400
{\an8}BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

383
00:27:33,151 --> 00:27:34,027
Makanlah.

384
00:27:34,861 --> 00:27:36,404
Pak cik!

385
00:27:36,488 --> 00:27:37,947
Hai, Da-bong.

386
00:27:38,031 --> 00:27:41,368
Pak cik selalu datang
masa kami makan sedap.

387
00:27:41,451 --> 00:27:42,619
Da-bong.

388
00:27:42,702 --> 00:27:44,162
Banyaknya kamu makan.

389
00:27:44,245 --> 00:27:47,082
Mak ingat kamu makan di luar.
Mak tak sediakan untuk kamu.

390
00:27:47,165 --> 00:27:49,000
Tak apa. Saya makan apa yang ada saja.

391
00:27:49,793 --> 00:27:51,461
- Sekejap.
- Mak…

392
00:27:55,382 --> 00:27:56,299
Mesti awak letih.

393
00:27:57,008 --> 00:27:59,094
- Kakak buatkan stu.
- Okey.

394
00:27:59,177 --> 00:28:01,554
Makan yang ini dulu.

395
00:28:03,014 --> 00:28:04,391
Aduh.

396
00:28:04,933 --> 00:28:07,519
Pak cik, kenapa tak makan perut khinzir?

397
00:28:07,602 --> 00:28:08,770
Sedaplah.

398
00:28:09,979 --> 00:28:11,231
Pak cik alergik.

399
00:28:11,314 --> 00:28:12,357
Kalau makan…

400
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,608
Jadi apa?

401
00:28:33,336 --> 00:28:35,171
Aduh…

402
00:28:36,214 --> 00:28:37,507
Tak tergambar.

403
00:28:38,967 --> 00:28:40,218
Mati pun tak apa.

404
00:28:47,058 --> 00:28:48,226
Awak…

405
00:28:48,810 --> 00:28:50,061
Apa?

406
00:28:50,145 --> 00:28:51,271
Awak tengok apa?

407
00:28:51,354 --> 00:28:53,440
Tak pernah tengok orang makan daging?

408
00:28:53,523 --> 00:28:54,983
Ya.

409
00:28:55,066 --> 00:28:57,068
Tak pernah tengok
Shin I-rang makan daging!

410
00:28:58,027 --> 00:28:58,903
Pak cik.

411
00:28:58,987 --> 00:29:00,697
Pipi pak cik merah.

412
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:02,282
Macam punggung monyet.

413
00:29:02,365 --> 00:29:03,199
Apa?

414
00:29:03,908 --> 00:29:04,743
Pipi pak cik?

415
00:29:04,826 --> 00:29:06,703
Hei! Aduh, budak ini.

416
00:29:07,954 --> 00:29:10,832
Kamu tak boleh makan khinzir!
Nanti naik ruam.

417
00:29:11,332 --> 00:29:14,169
Tengok muka kamu. Dah merah.

418
00:29:19,883 --> 00:29:22,218
- I-rang.
- Aduhai.

419
00:29:24,179 --> 00:29:26,765
Kenapa buat aku begini?

420
00:29:27,515 --> 00:29:29,642
Kenapa selalu susahkan aku?

421
00:29:30,143 --> 00:29:32,812
Tolonglah jangan kacau aku!

422
00:29:34,105 --> 00:29:38,276
"Dia hidup bersama haiwan liar,

423
00:29:39,277 --> 00:29:42,405
dan malaikat…

424
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:44,783
bertemu dengannya."

425
00:29:46,326 --> 00:29:48,036
"Selepas John ditangkap…"

426
00:29:50,121 --> 00:29:51,706
Kau nak apa daripada aku?

427
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:53,917
Kau ini siapa sebenarnya?

428
00:29:54,501 --> 00:29:55,376
Saya pun tak tahu.

429
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:57,545
Tak habis-habis.

430
00:29:58,463 --> 00:30:00,590
Begini. Alang-alang encik peguam,

431
00:30:01,341 --> 00:30:03,134
boleh encik siasat siapa saya?

432
00:30:03,218 --> 00:30:04,219
Kenapa pula?

433
00:30:04,803 --> 00:30:07,388
Bulan depan, aku dah kena bayar sewa.

434
00:30:08,181 --> 00:30:10,141
Kalau tak, mak aku mengamuk.

435
00:30:10,642 --> 00:30:12,685
Pergi cari duit untuk aku atau…

436
00:30:13,269 --> 00:30:14,854
bawa nombor ekor bertuah.

437
00:30:14,938 --> 00:30:17,232
Kalau saya ada kuasa begitu,

438
00:30:17,315 --> 00:30:20,235
dah lama saya beli bangunan
di alam hantu.

439
00:30:20,318 --> 00:30:22,946
Jadi, kau cuma boleh usik aku?

440
00:30:23,988 --> 00:30:25,406
Sedihnya.

441
00:30:28,535 --> 00:30:29,828
<i>Hantu?</i>

442
00:30:30,411 --> 00:30:32,247
Saya rasa saya dirasuk di rumah bomoh.

443
00:30:33,206 --> 00:30:36,334
Bomoh itu dibawa ke hospital,
tapi kemudian dia hilang.

444
00:30:37,001 --> 00:30:38,837
Dia lari dan tak bayar bil hospital.

445
00:30:39,838 --> 00:30:41,798
Macam mana awak nampak hantu itu?

446
00:30:42,382 --> 00:30:44,801
Ada satu meja yang bomoh itu tinggalkan.

447
00:30:45,385 --> 00:30:47,720
Saya jumpa kemenyan lama di dalam laci.

448
00:30:52,642 --> 00:30:53,685
Sejuk.

449
00:30:58,231 --> 00:30:59,357
Sejuknya.

450
00:31:00,066 --> 00:31:00,900
Pelik.

451
00:31:01,484 --> 00:31:04,529
Biasanya, badan akan terpulas
atau air suci berasap.

452
00:31:05,154 --> 00:31:07,073
Ini bukan hantu biasa.

453
00:31:07,156 --> 00:31:09,325
Dia baca Bible,
suka perut khinzir dengan soju…

454
00:31:09,409 --> 00:31:11,286
Kopi pun dia minum.

455
00:31:11,369 --> 00:31:12,829
Mungkin itu yang dia suka dulu.

456
00:31:12,912 --> 00:31:14,581
Orang dirasuk

457
00:31:14,664 --> 00:31:17,083
apabila keinginan mereka memuncak.

458
00:31:17,959 --> 00:31:21,421
Apabila ada sesuatu cetuskan kegembiraan,
macam makanan atau lagu kesukaan,

459
00:31:21,504 --> 00:31:22,589
atau sebaliknya,

460
00:31:22,672 --> 00:31:24,382
apabila jumpa orang yang dibenci,

461
00:31:24,465 --> 00:31:27,844
atau sesuatu yang timbulkan kemarahan,
kemungkinan untuk dirasuk meningkat.

462
00:31:28,928 --> 00:31:30,430
Apabila kita dirasuk,

463
00:31:30,513 --> 00:31:32,765
kita berkelakuan pelik,

464
00:31:32,849 --> 00:31:35,351
tapi kita tak ingat pun

465
00:31:36,561 --> 00:31:37,937
apa kita dah buat.

466
00:31:38,021 --> 00:31:39,856
Maknanya saya dalam bahaya.

467
00:31:39,939 --> 00:31:40,982
Bahaya atau tak,

468
00:31:41,608 --> 00:31:44,777
kita pergi tengok Bangunan Okcheon dulu.

469
00:31:48,197 --> 00:31:49,741
Aduh!

470
00:31:53,494 --> 00:31:54,787
Saya dah agak.

471
00:31:55,705 --> 00:31:58,666
Azimat ini yang seru hantu.

472
00:31:59,626 --> 00:32:02,253
Kalau saya bakar azimat ini,

473
00:32:02,337 --> 00:32:03,463
hantu akan hilang?

474
00:32:04,923 --> 00:32:05,757
Mungkin.

475
00:32:06,799 --> 00:32:07,842
Jangan.

476
00:32:07,926 --> 00:32:09,802
Aku nak kenal diri sendiri dulu!

477
00:32:09,886 --> 00:32:11,679
Kau tak boleh buat apa-apa.

478
00:32:13,598 --> 00:32:15,475
Dia di sini sekarang? Dia kata apa?

479
00:32:15,558 --> 00:32:16,851
Apa yang dia cakap?

480
00:32:16,935 --> 00:32:19,729
Dia sibuk suruh saya siasat siapa dia.

481
00:32:19,812 --> 00:32:22,190
Jadi, apa kata
awak siasat siapa hantu ini?

482
00:32:22,774 --> 00:32:24,984
Hantu lebih senang pergi
kalau kita tahu kisahnya.

483
00:32:25,068 --> 00:32:28,154
Siasat aku!

484
00:32:28,237 --> 00:32:29,072
Siasat…

485
00:32:30,615 --> 00:32:32,951
Kalau saya nak tolong pun,

486
00:32:33,034 --> 00:32:34,619
saya tak tahu macam mana.

487
00:32:34,702 --> 00:32:37,038
Kalau awak tahu nama dan tarikh lahir dia,

488
00:32:37,121 --> 00:32:38,373
ingatan dia boleh pulih.

489
00:32:38,915 --> 00:32:39,749
Betulkah?

490
00:32:40,333 --> 00:32:42,877
Macam mana awak tahu?

491
00:32:42,961 --> 00:32:44,128
Dulu…

492
00:32:45,421 --> 00:32:47,590
saya bomoh.

493
00:32:55,932 --> 00:32:58,810
Seruan Tuhan yang bawa saya

494
00:33:00,061 --> 00:33:01,396
ke jalan ini.

495
00:33:05,692 --> 00:33:08,903
Sebenarnya, tak susah pun
nak siasat siapa dia.

496
00:33:09,779 --> 00:33:12,240
Awak cari saja orang yang jumpa bomoh itu.

497
00:33:12,323 --> 00:33:14,867
Mesti dia yang nak seru hantu itu.

498
00:33:14,951 --> 00:33:16,035
Yalah.

499
00:33:16,786 --> 00:33:19,038
Saya nampak ada CCTV di koridor.

500
00:33:26,462 --> 00:33:27,714
Ini saja?

501
00:33:28,548 --> 00:33:29,882
Bahannya tak cukup.

502
00:33:30,466 --> 00:33:31,718
Kita tak perlukan bahan.

503
00:33:32,468 --> 00:33:34,012
Keluarga si mati pilih pampasan.

504
00:33:35,263 --> 00:33:36,723
Saya nak awak ikut saja.

505
00:33:36,806 --> 00:33:39,142
Penyelesaian secara aman itu yang terbaik,

506
00:33:39,726 --> 00:33:41,519
tapi manalah tahu ada masalah,

507
00:33:41,602 --> 00:33:43,813
lebih baik saya dapatkan
tandatangan mereka.

508
00:33:44,439 --> 00:33:45,481
Itu lebih baik.

509
00:33:49,694 --> 00:33:51,529
SUKARELAWAN SARANG

510
00:33:53,072 --> 00:33:55,033
Perempuan ini klien terakhir dia.

511
00:33:55,575 --> 00:33:56,701
Tengok di sini.

512
00:33:57,493 --> 00:33:59,245
Dia datang beberapa kali.

513
00:33:59,954 --> 00:34:02,498
Encik, bila rakaman ini?

514
00:34:03,166 --> 00:34:04,083
Itu?

515
00:34:04,167 --> 00:34:05,418
Itu suapan langsung.

516
00:34:05,501 --> 00:34:06,627
Apa?

517
00:34:06,711 --> 00:34:10,715
Maknanya, perempuan itu berdiri
di depan Unit 501 sekarang.

518
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:18,723
Boleh saya bantu puan?

519
00:34:18,806 --> 00:34:20,266
Boleh.

520
00:34:21,434 --> 00:34:24,729
Dulu ini rumah tok bomoh…

521
00:34:25,897 --> 00:34:28,524
Bomoh itu pindah sebab sakit.

522
00:34:29,192 --> 00:34:30,193
Saya tahu.

523
00:34:30,693 --> 00:34:34,280
Saya ada dengan dia semasa dia pengsan.

524
00:34:38,493 --> 00:34:40,328
<i>Saya yang telefon ambulans.</i>

525
00:34:41,537 --> 00:34:43,623
Saya datang nak tanya khabar.

526
00:34:43,706 --> 00:34:47,335
Tapi saya tengok dah jadi firma guaman,
sebab itu saya masuk.

527
00:34:49,295 --> 00:34:53,466
Puan datang jumpa bomoh itu
berkenaan suami puan?

528
00:34:54,509 --> 00:34:56,135
Macam mana encik tahu?

529
00:34:56,219 --> 00:34:58,554
Puan boleh ceritakan semuanya kepada saya.

530
00:34:59,931 --> 00:35:03,267
Memang kerja peguam dan bomoh
dengar kisah penganiayaan.

531
00:35:09,065 --> 00:35:10,024
Beberapa bulan…

532
00:35:12,777 --> 00:35:13,820
Beberapa bulan lepas,

533
00:35:15,113 --> 00:35:19,242
suami saya jalani pembedahan
di Hospital Cheongil.

534
00:35:20,201 --> 00:35:21,327
Dia alami kejutan

535
00:35:22,036 --> 00:35:23,621
semasa pembedahan.

536
00:35:24,664 --> 00:35:27,917
Sebab itu puan jumpa bomoh?

537
00:35:28,501 --> 00:35:30,378
Ucapkan selamat tinggal
buat kali terakhir?

538
00:35:30,461 --> 00:35:31,504
Tak.

539
00:35:32,922 --> 00:35:34,006
Selepas itu,

540
00:35:36,175 --> 00:35:38,177
anak perempuan saya
tak nak keluar dari bilik.

541
00:35:42,014 --> 00:35:42,974
Buka pintu.

542
00:35:43,891 --> 00:35:46,561
<i>- Ayah dia yang sihat mati mengejut.</i>
- Buka.

543
00:35:47,854 --> 00:35:49,105
<i>Mesti dia terkejut.</i>

544
00:35:49,188 --> 00:35:50,523
Cakaplah dengan mak.

545
00:35:57,196 --> 00:35:58,072
Ji-woo!

546
00:36:01,159 --> 00:36:04,162
Mak janji tak buat lagi, tolonglah.

547
00:36:12,128 --> 00:36:14,714
<i>Lima bulan dia berkurung di dalam bilik.</i>

548
00:36:16,424 --> 00:36:17,508
<i>Puas saya pujuk dia.</i>

549
00:36:18,551 --> 00:36:21,387
<i>Cakap lembut, marah dan menangis.</i>

550
00:36:23,431 --> 00:36:24,640
<i>Tapi tak berjaya.</i>

551
00:36:29,687 --> 00:36:30,521
Tapi,

552
00:36:32,398 --> 00:36:33,900
saya rasa lega sikit

553
00:36:34,859 --> 00:36:36,235
luahkan kepada encik.

554
00:36:38,571 --> 00:36:39,739
Terima kasih.

555
00:36:42,408 --> 00:36:45,286
Nama saya. Nama dan tarikh lahir saya.

556
00:36:46,287 --> 00:36:47,538
Boleh puan beritahu saya

557
00:36:49,624 --> 00:36:52,585
nama dan tarikh lahir suami puan?

558
00:36:53,252 --> 00:36:55,838
Nama dia Lee Gang-pung.

559
00:36:57,423 --> 00:36:58,883
Dia lahir

560
00:37:00,092 --> 00:37:02,178
pada 25 April 1980.

561
00:37:22,657 --> 00:37:24,659
Anak mak dah bangun.

562
00:37:32,041 --> 00:37:33,584
Kamu cantik macam mak.

563
00:37:34,627 --> 00:37:36,170
<i>Saya dah jadi ayah.</i>

564
00:37:42,551 --> 00:37:44,011
Terima kasih.

565
00:37:44,095 --> 00:37:45,888
Tengok. Macam pengantin baru.

566
00:37:45,972 --> 00:37:47,223
Hati-hati.

567
00:37:47,306 --> 00:37:48,766
{\an8}SUKARELAWAN SARANG

568
00:37:51,352 --> 00:37:52,311
Bingo!

569
00:37:52,395 --> 00:37:53,229
Suka tak?

570
00:38:10,288 --> 00:38:11,205
Min-ju!

571
00:38:20,172 --> 00:38:21,299
Mesti awak

572
00:38:22,341 --> 00:38:25,052
banyak bergelut seorang diri.

573
00:38:37,398 --> 00:38:38,482
Kau dah gila?

574
00:38:46,782 --> 00:38:48,701
Kenapa dia tampar aku?

575
00:39:05,509 --> 00:39:08,512
Apa jadi tadi?

576
00:39:09,096 --> 00:39:09,972
Saya…

577
00:39:11,682 --> 00:39:12,808
dah ingat.

578
00:39:14,769 --> 00:39:15,770
Yakah?

579
00:39:16,395 --> 00:39:17,730
Saat kematian saya.

580
00:39:18,522 --> 00:39:20,941
Sila berikan bius.

581
00:39:23,944 --> 00:39:25,446
Dia dah pengsan.

582
00:39:33,913 --> 00:39:36,374
Saluran udara tersekat.
Kena buat pembedahan kecemasan!

583
00:39:39,293 --> 00:39:41,253
- Aduh!
- Kita nak buat trakeostomi?

584
00:39:41,337 --> 00:39:43,255
- Doktor!
- Diam!

585
00:39:43,339 --> 00:39:44,757
Biar saya uruskan, okey?

586
00:39:56,185 --> 00:39:57,186
Rahsiakan hal ini.

587
00:39:59,605 --> 00:40:02,108
Cakap dia mati sebab kejutan
daripada jantung terhenti.

588
00:40:05,444 --> 00:40:06,987
Ada satu suara yang jelas…

589
00:40:08,989 --> 00:40:11,283
yang suruh cakap
itu kematian disebabkan kejutan.

590
00:40:25,423 --> 00:40:27,466
Tak pernah masukkan baju
ke dalam mesin basuh.

591
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:49,113
PERMOHONAN KERJA
NAMA: SHIN I-RANG

592
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:24,064
Kenapa kamu belum tidur?

593
00:41:24,148 --> 00:41:25,941
Saya tak boleh tidur.

594
00:41:27,401 --> 00:41:28,777
Saya nak masuk tidur.

595
00:41:29,570 --> 00:41:31,155
Mak nak minum.

596
00:41:32,156 --> 00:41:33,199
Nak minum sekali?

597
00:41:34,241 --> 00:41:35,826
Tak ada snek minum.

598
00:41:37,036 --> 00:41:39,038
Soju paling sedap diminum begitu saja.

599
00:41:45,002 --> 00:41:46,212
Minum.

600
00:41:58,265 --> 00:41:59,225
I-rang.

601
00:42:00,184 --> 00:42:01,393
Hidup kamu susah sekarang?

602
00:42:04,355 --> 00:42:06,190
Bila hidup saya pernah senang?

603
00:42:08,442 --> 00:42:10,945
Lima tahun baru dapat lesen guaman.

604
00:42:12,571 --> 00:42:13,656
Cari kerja pun susah.

605
00:42:15,282 --> 00:42:17,618
Tapi kamu masih dapat kerja.

606
00:42:19,620 --> 00:42:21,580
Betul, tapi…

607
00:42:23,999 --> 00:42:27,378
Berapa kos nak buka firma guaman?

608
00:42:29,755 --> 00:42:33,926
Senior kamu, Jeong-su
pun dah beli bangunan.

609
00:42:34,009 --> 00:42:35,177
Mak nak cakap apa?

610
00:42:35,886 --> 00:42:37,930
Mak cakap saya lembik,
tak mampu buka firma.

611
00:42:38,013 --> 00:42:40,891
Mak cakap begitu

612
00:42:40,975 --> 00:42:43,269
sebab tak nak kamu tak sedar diri.

613
00:42:46,272 --> 00:42:48,023
Saya tak cukup duit.

614
00:42:48,107 --> 00:42:51,610
Mak boleh guna duit deposit sikit.

615
00:42:52,778 --> 00:42:54,863
Deposit mak 200 juta won.

616
00:42:54,947 --> 00:42:56,073
Sekejap.

617
00:42:56,156 --> 00:42:58,075
Tak apa.

618
00:42:58,158 --> 00:42:59,118
Mak.

619
00:42:59,201 --> 00:43:01,704
Saya suka kerja sekarang.

620
00:43:04,540 --> 00:43:05,874
I-rang.

621
00:43:05,958 --> 00:43:06,875
Ya?

622
00:43:06,959 --> 00:43:09,295
Kamu tahu mak percayakan kamu, bukan?

623
00:43:11,463 --> 00:43:13,299
Ya, tahu.

624
00:43:13,382 --> 00:43:15,718
Mak tak tahu apa masalah kamu sekarang,

625
00:43:17,011 --> 00:43:18,429
tapi buatlah ikut suka kamu.

626
00:43:18,512 --> 00:43:20,055
Mak sokong kamu.

627
00:43:23,225 --> 00:43:25,269
Aduh, mak.

628
00:43:26,228 --> 00:43:27,771
Baru sebotol soju dah mabuk.

629
00:43:29,356 --> 00:43:31,609
Okey. Pergilah tidur.

630
00:43:32,651 --> 00:43:33,527
Okey.

631
00:43:34,069 --> 00:43:35,821
Kamu pun kena tidur.

632
00:43:35,904 --> 00:43:36,739
Okey.

633
00:44:06,852 --> 00:44:09,355
FIRMA GUAMAN TAEBAEK

634
00:44:10,272 --> 00:44:12,775
Tak seronoknya selesai begini.

635
00:44:15,319 --> 00:44:17,488
Kamu tahu berapa saya bayar kamu?

636
00:44:18,405 --> 00:44:20,741
Keluarga si mati
sedang tandatangan perjanjian.

637
00:44:21,367 --> 00:44:22,284
PERJANJIAN PAMPASAN

638
00:44:22,368 --> 00:44:24,161
Pn. Kim, puan beruntung.

639
00:44:24,745 --> 00:44:27,831
Doktor tak bunuh pun suami puan,

640
00:44:27,915 --> 00:44:31,085
tapi demi tanggungjawab moral,
dia tawarkan 30 juta won.

641
00:44:31,168 --> 00:44:33,671
Siasatan polis belum habis.

642
00:44:33,754 --> 00:44:34,880
Kalau dah habis?

643
00:44:35,714 --> 00:44:36,590
Bawa ke mahkamah?

644
00:44:37,174 --> 00:44:39,218
- Ya, kalau perlu.
- Aduhai.

645
00:44:40,219 --> 00:44:42,429
Kenapa puan nak rumitkan keadaan?

646
00:44:43,472 --> 00:44:44,640
Cakap memang senang.

647
00:44:44,723 --> 00:44:47,559
Bukan senang nak buktikan
amalan salah perubatan.

648
00:44:48,143 --> 00:44:50,646
Kalau tersilap langkah,
puan boleh hilang rumah.

649
00:44:51,772 --> 00:44:54,024
Saya dengar anak puan sakit.

650
00:44:54,108 --> 00:44:57,486
Macam mana kalau puan dan anak puan
terpaksa merempat di jalanan?

651
00:44:57,569 --> 00:44:58,654
Aduhai.

652
00:44:58,737 --> 00:45:02,116
Peguam Han, tolong cakap kalau saya salah.

653
00:45:04,743 --> 00:45:07,621
Nyawa mendiang suami puan tak ternilai,

654
00:45:07,704 --> 00:45:09,915
tapi puan terimalah
sebagai tanda keikhlasan.

655
00:45:10,624 --> 00:45:13,210
Tapi keputusan di tangan puan.

656
00:45:14,545 --> 00:45:15,963
Boleh saya baca dulu?

657
00:45:16,046 --> 00:45:20,175
Puan boleh baca kalau tak percayakan saya,

658
00:45:20,259 --> 00:45:22,636
tapi bolehkah puan faham?

659
00:45:24,346 --> 00:45:27,391
Biasalah pihak yang nak selesaikan
baca perjanjian.

660
00:45:28,308 --> 00:45:29,560
Jaga adab awak.

661
00:45:31,145 --> 00:45:32,521
Tak apalah.

662
00:45:33,021 --> 00:45:34,690
Mesti peguam dah semak betul-betul.

663
00:45:35,732 --> 00:45:38,110
Betul. Tandatangan di sini.

664
00:45:40,028 --> 00:45:42,364
KIM MIN…

665
00:45:44,324 --> 00:45:45,742
Maaf mengganggu.

666
00:45:49,621 --> 00:45:51,248
Apa En. Shin buat di sini?

667
00:45:51,331 --> 00:45:52,749
Puan ingat saya lagi.

668
00:45:52,833 --> 00:45:54,877
Puan peguam En. Lee Jeong-seok?

669
00:45:58,589 --> 00:46:01,175
Harap saya tak terlambat.

670
00:46:01,258 --> 00:46:02,134
Saya ambil, ya?

671
00:46:03,010 --> 00:46:04,678
Baguslah.

672
00:46:04,761 --> 00:46:05,596
Sekejap.

673
00:46:05,679 --> 00:46:07,514
Awak kenal dia?

674
00:46:08,557 --> 00:46:11,018
Siapa awak nak…

675
00:46:11,101 --> 00:46:13,770
Nanti awak kenallah saya.

676
00:46:13,854 --> 00:46:15,981
Saya nak cakap tentang awak dulu.

677
00:46:16,732 --> 00:46:18,108
Peguam Byeon Seung-jun.

678
00:46:18,192 --> 00:46:20,861
Selepas Institut Penyelidikan
dan Latihan Kehakiman 2017,

679
00:46:20,944 --> 00:46:24,948
awak bekerja di Taebaek
selama lima tahun tiga bulan

680
00:46:25,032 --> 00:46:26,700
sampai Julai 2022.

681
00:46:28,827 --> 00:46:31,246
Ya, kenapa? Apa masalahnya?

682
00:46:31,872 --> 00:46:36,126
Taebaek ini firma guaman impian
setiap peguam.

683
00:46:36,210 --> 00:46:37,252
Ya, betul.

684
00:46:37,336 --> 00:46:39,087
Bidang ini sangat kecil

685
00:46:39,171 --> 00:46:42,049
sampai kita boleh berkawan
dengan peguam pihak satu lagi.

686
00:46:42,132 --> 00:46:45,093
Macam mencurigakan saja.

687
00:46:45,177 --> 00:46:46,053
Jadi,

688
00:46:46,970 --> 00:46:48,514
apa awak nak cakap sebenarnya?

689
00:46:48,597 --> 00:46:53,060
Rupa-rupanya, Peguam Byeon
dan Rakan Kongsi Urusan Yang Do-gyeong

690
00:46:55,145 --> 00:46:56,813
main golf bersama hujung minggu lepas

691
00:46:57,564 --> 00:46:59,191
dan berbincang senyap-senyap.

692
00:46:59,775 --> 00:47:01,985
Hei, awak ekori saya?

693
00:47:02,069 --> 00:47:02,986
Saya?

694
00:47:03,070 --> 00:47:04,821
Mestilah tak.

695
00:47:11,328 --> 00:47:12,371
Opocot!

696
00:47:14,665 --> 00:47:16,083
En. Lee, tahniah.

697
00:47:17,709 --> 00:47:20,963
Awak menang khidmat guaman percuma
pada majlis pembukaan pejabat saya.

698
00:47:23,757 --> 00:47:24,883
En. Peguam.

699
00:47:26,051 --> 00:47:28,262
Saya pandai juga,
awak boleh harapkan saya.

700
00:47:29,096 --> 00:47:29,972
Terima kasih.

701
00:47:31,723 --> 00:47:32,933
Tapi apa kita nak buat?

702
00:47:33,016 --> 00:47:36,061
Isteri saya dah upah peguam.

703
00:47:36,144 --> 00:47:37,813
Saya dah siasat.

704
00:47:37,896 --> 00:47:39,690
Peguam dia ada banyak masalah.

705
00:47:39,773 --> 00:47:42,317
Dia takkan bela isteri awak.

706
00:47:42,901 --> 00:47:43,777
Apa kita nak buat?

707
00:47:43,860 --> 00:47:45,153
Apa lagi?

708
00:47:45,237 --> 00:47:46,280
Kita buat dia dipecat.

709
00:47:47,614 --> 00:47:50,659
Macam hantu, seorang pun tak tahu.

710
00:47:59,209 --> 00:48:00,419
Maaf.

711
00:48:01,086 --> 00:48:02,004
Awak buat apa?

712
00:48:02,087 --> 00:48:05,716
Sekejap.
Kita akan mulakan perjanjian sebenar.

713
00:48:07,217 --> 00:48:08,635
Ini dia.

714
00:48:08,719 --> 00:48:10,929
Helo, En. Yang. Ini saya.

715
00:48:11,013 --> 00:48:14,766
<i>Peguam sentiasa suka tinggalkan</i>
<i>bahan bukti yang membantu.</i>

716
00:48:14,850 --> 00:48:17,019
Encik masukkan duit
ke akaun nama saya, bukan?

717
00:48:17,102 --> 00:48:18,395
<i>Awak dah pujuk Kim Min-ju?</i>

718
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:22,149
Bukan senang nak kurangkan
jumlah pampasan.

719
00:48:22,232 --> 00:48:23,066
Sebab…

720
00:48:23,150 --> 00:48:24,443
…<i>kalau bukan sebab saya,</i>

721
00:48:25,068 --> 00:48:26,987
<i>klien encik terpaksa bayar</i>
<i>satu bilion won.</i>

722
00:48:28,572 --> 00:48:29,531
Penipu!

723
00:48:30,157 --> 00:48:31,158
Tergamak…

724
00:48:31,241 --> 00:48:34,369
Ini boleh buat awak hilang lesen.

725
00:48:35,037 --> 00:48:36,288
Berat kesalahan ini.

726
00:48:36,371 --> 00:48:38,415
Sekejap.

727
00:48:38,498 --> 00:48:41,001
Saya boleh jelaskan semuanya.

728
00:48:41,668 --> 00:48:44,087
Peguam Han, awak nak ke mana? Peguam Han.

729
00:48:46,673 --> 00:48:49,593
Ada lagi sebab untuk saya tunggu?

730
00:49:00,187 --> 00:49:01,813
Kami tak nak dengar penjelasan awak.

731
00:49:01,897 --> 00:49:04,358
Tarik diri sekarang.

732
00:49:04,441 --> 00:49:07,778
Pindahkan dua kali ganda
komisen yang awak dapat

733
00:49:07,861 --> 00:49:09,404
ke akaun Pn. Kim.

734
00:49:10,572 --> 00:49:11,698
Faham?

735
00:49:15,827 --> 00:49:16,870
Peguam Shin.

736
00:49:18,330 --> 00:49:19,414
Terima kasih.

737
00:49:24,127 --> 00:49:26,338
Apa puan nak buat sekarang?

738
00:49:27,089 --> 00:49:28,465
Puan akan saman, bukan?

739
00:49:28,965 --> 00:49:31,468
Kalau saya saman, tapi ada masalah…

740
00:49:33,261 --> 00:49:36,640
Puan rasa kenapa anak puan
berkurung di dalam bilik dia?

741
00:49:38,350 --> 00:49:39,184
Apa?

742
00:49:39,267 --> 00:49:42,896
Mungkin dia marah dengan keadaan sekarang.

743
00:49:44,398 --> 00:49:47,734
Sudahlah ayah dia mati
disebabkan pembedahan biasa,

744
00:49:49,403 --> 00:49:50,862
tapi mak dia pula nak putus asa

745
00:49:51,780 --> 00:49:53,281
tanpa bicarakan di mahkamah.

746
00:50:00,831 --> 00:50:01,790
Saya faham…

747
00:50:02,916 --> 00:50:04,084
perasaan itu.

748
00:50:05,919 --> 00:50:07,754
<i>Dia tahu</i>

749
00:50:08,922 --> 00:50:11,758
<i>mak dia yang paling merana</i>
<i>selepas ayah dia mati mengejut.</i>

750
00:50:12,259 --> 00:50:14,219
Macam mana temu duga?

751
00:50:17,180 --> 00:50:19,766
Ya, rasanya okey.

752
00:50:20,809 --> 00:50:22,728
<i>Dia tak sampai hati nak cakap begitu.</i>

753
00:50:25,439 --> 00:50:26,773
Saya rasa,

754
00:50:27,691 --> 00:50:29,651
eloklah puan tanya apa Ji-woo rasa.

755
00:50:44,458 --> 00:50:47,461
JI-WOO

756
00:50:55,510 --> 00:50:57,220
Begini, Ji-woo.

757
00:51:02,392 --> 00:51:04,269
Kematian ayah…

758
00:51:08,523 --> 00:51:09,941
bukan kemalangan.

759
00:51:11,860 --> 00:51:15,614
Doktor dia buat silap semasa pembedahan,

760
00:51:18,158 --> 00:51:20,410
sebab itu ayah mati.

761
00:51:23,038 --> 00:51:24,164
Mak nak

762
00:51:25,499 --> 00:51:28,460
hukum doktor yang buat ayah kamu begitu.

763
00:51:31,087 --> 00:51:32,506
Apa kamu rasa?

764
00:52:01,910 --> 00:52:02,869
Menang.

765
00:52:07,207 --> 00:52:08,166
Ji-woo.

766
00:52:09,876 --> 00:52:10,877
Apa kamu kata?

767
00:52:13,547 --> 00:52:15,215
Menang perbicaraan itu.

768
00:52:22,264 --> 00:52:23,139
Okey.

769
00:52:23,974 --> 00:52:26,393
Mak akan menang

770
00:52:26,977 --> 00:52:32,274
dan hukum semua orang
yang buat ayah kamu mati.

771
00:52:53,128 --> 00:52:54,462
KIM MIN-JU

772
00:52:58,216 --> 00:52:59,759
Ya, Shin I-rang bercakap.

773
00:53:00,343 --> 00:53:01,678
Saya nak teruskan.

774
00:53:01,761 --> 00:53:05,432
Saya nak lawan demi Gang-pung dan Ji-woo.

775
00:53:07,434 --> 00:53:08,727
Bagus keputusan puan.

776
00:53:10,061 --> 00:53:10,979
Saya

777
00:53:12,522 --> 00:53:14,232
akan buat yang terbaik.

778
00:53:37,839 --> 00:53:38,924
Saya dibawa ke sini,

779
00:53:39,007 --> 00:53:41,259
ucapkan selamat tinggal kepada keluarga,

780
00:53:41,343 --> 00:53:42,427
masuk ke bilik bedah.

781
00:53:43,136 --> 00:53:45,680
Ada lima orang di dalam…

782
00:53:47,390 --> 00:53:48,683
- Helo.
- Boleh saya bantu?

783
00:53:48,767 --> 00:53:50,060
Boleh saya tengok di dalam?

784
00:53:50,143 --> 00:53:51,770
- Sekejap saja.
- Tak boleh.

785
00:53:51,853 --> 00:53:53,313
- Sila pergi.
- Sekejap.

786
00:53:53,396 --> 00:53:54,397
- Cepatlah.
- Pergi.

787
00:53:54,481 --> 00:53:56,399
- Sekejap, saya…
- Encik kena keluar.

788
00:53:58,443 --> 00:53:59,569
Saya bukan orang jahat!

789
00:54:07,786 --> 00:54:10,747
HOSPITAL CHEONGIL

790
00:54:13,041 --> 00:54:14,542
Tak menjadi pula.

791
00:54:15,085 --> 00:54:16,002
Ya.

792
00:54:18,838 --> 00:54:20,256
Helo.

793
00:54:20,340 --> 00:54:22,676
Saya pemeriksa
dari Persatuan Hospital Korea.

794
00:54:23,259 --> 00:54:25,553
Saya datang nak buat
kaji selidik untuk perbaiki

795
00:54:25,637 --> 00:54:27,681
persekitaran kerja pekerja hospital.

796
00:54:27,764 --> 00:54:29,516
Okey. Sila ikut saya.

797
00:54:29,599 --> 00:54:30,558
Ya.

798
00:54:35,271 --> 00:54:38,900
Kami terima laporan yang hak pekerja
tak dilindungi di hospital ini

799
00:54:38,984 --> 00:54:40,610
disebabkan kekurangan sumber.

800
00:54:41,194 --> 00:54:44,280
Saya nak senarai pengambilan
dan pemecatan pekerja enam bulan ini.

801
00:54:45,407 --> 00:54:46,241
Itu…

802
00:54:48,743 --> 00:54:51,913
Dari 2019 hingga 2024.

803
00:54:51,997 --> 00:54:53,873
AGENSI DETEKTIF PERSENDIRIAN IDAMAN

804
00:54:57,919 --> 00:54:59,087
PENGGERA

805
00:55:16,146 --> 00:55:18,064
PETISYEN

806
00:55:38,585 --> 00:55:41,254
Tahniah atas perbicaraan pertama!

807
00:55:42,714 --> 00:55:45,508
Tahniah!

808
00:55:48,219 --> 00:55:49,971
Mesti awak menang. Awak boleh!

809
00:55:50,555 --> 00:55:52,348
Pak cik, bunuh mereka semua.

810
00:55:52,891 --> 00:55:54,934
Da-bong, tak elok cakap begitu.

811
00:56:04,402 --> 00:56:06,154
Segaknya kamu, I-rang.

812
00:56:06,237 --> 00:56:07,280
Semoga berjaya.

813
00:56:07,363 --> 00:56:09,157
Jaga adab di mahkamah.

814
00:56:10,492 --> 00:56:12,869
Jangan risau. Saya baik-baik saja.

815
00:56:15,622 --> 00:56:16,956
Saya dah lewat. Pergi dulu.

816
00:56:17,040 --> 00:56:19,667
- Aduh, okey. Kita pun kena cepat.
- Okey.

817
00:56:19,751 --> 00:56:21,878
Kamu semua nak ke mana?

818
00:56:21,961 --> 00:56:23,129
Ke mana lagi?

819
00:56:23,213 --> 00:56:25,465
Kami nak pergi tengok
perbicaraan pertama kamu.

820
00:56:25,548 --> 00:56:27,801
Hore, seronoknya!

821
00:56:27,884 --> 00:56:30,053
Kamu tak pergi, Da-bong.
Kamu kena ke tadika.

822
00:56:31,012 --> 00:56:33,556
Awak pergilah.
Kami hantar dia ke tadika dulu.

823
00:56:33,640 --> 00:56:36,935
- Jom?
- Selamat berjaya, pak cik.

824
00:56:42,065 --> 00:56:43,191
Tengok perbicaraan?

825
00:56:44,109 --> 00:56:45,860
Ini bukan Liga Perdana.

826
00:56:46,778 --> 00:56:49,280
{\an8}MAHKAMAH KOREA

827
00:56:52,117 --> 00:56:54,119
{\an8}MEJA PLAINTIF

828
00:57:01,543 --> 00:57:04,045
Jangan risau. Semua baik-baik saja.

829
00:57:04,629 --> 00:57:05,547
Okey.

830
00:57:24,399 --> 00:57:25,483
I-rang.

831
00:57:30,822 --> 00:57:32,949
Yang pertama inilah mereka nak tengok.

832
00:57:42,333 --> 00:57:44,335
MAHKAMAH KOREA

833
00:57:47,464 --> 00:57:49,215
<i>Awak tunggu di sini, Gang-pung.</i>

834
00:57:49,299 --> 00:57:51,551
Saya tak nak awak marah
semasa perbicaraan.

835
00:57:54,762 --> 00:57:57,348
<i>Saya nak soal defendan sendiri,</i>
<i>Lee Jeong-seok.</i>

836
00:57:58,057 --> 00:57:58,975
<i>Diterima.</i>

837
00:57:59,642 --> 00:58:01,728
<i>Defendan, sila ke kandang saksi.</i>

838
00:58:09,736 --> 00:58:11,112
Terkejut saya.

839
00:58:11,988 --> 00:58:13,948
Kenapa masuk?
Saya suruh awak tunggu di luar.

840
00:58:14,657 --> 00:58:16,784
{\an8}Peguam Shin, semuanya okey?

841
00:58:16,868 --> 00:58:17,952
{\an8}Saya bersumpah…

842
00:58:18,036 --> 00:58:20,163
{\an8}- Leher gatal pula.
- …untuk bercakap benar

843
00:58:20,246 --> 00:58:22,790
tanpa berahsia atau menokok tambah,

844
00:58:23,416 --> 00:58:26,753
- dan jika saya menipu…
- Ada sesuatu yang saya belum cakap.

845
00:58:27,337 --> 00:58:28,463
Nantilah. Saya sibuk.

846
00:58:28,546 --> 00:58:30,131
Saya rasa penting.

847
00:58:32,800 --> 00:58:33,968
Bedebah itu…

848
00:58:38,556 --> 00:58:39,974
Anak haram.

849
00:58:40,058 --> 00:58:41,601
Jangan marah.

850
00:58:42,644 --> 00:58:45,271
Defendan membedah En. Lee Gang-pung

851
00:58:45,355 --> 00:58:47,190
pada 13 Oktober tahun lepas, betul?

852
00:58:47,941 --> 00:58:49,150
Ya.

853
00:58:49,234 --> 00:58:52,028
Boleh encik jelaskan situasi ketika itu?

854
00:58:52,779 --> 00:58:54,822
Pembedahan dengkur biasa saja.

855
00:58:55,657 --> 00:58:57,700
Tak ada apa-apa yang pelik.

856
00:58:59,536 --> 00:59:01,454
Menurut dokumen hospital,

857
00:59:01,538 --> 00:59:05,291
kes En. Lee memerlukan
perubahan struktur saluran udaranya.

858
00:59:05,375 --> 00:59:07,293
Jadi, bius am itu mandatori.

859
00:59:07,377 --> 00:59:08,211
Betul.

860
00:59:08,294 --> 00:59:10,547
Tapi ada satu masalah.

861
00:59:10,630 --> 00:59:11,881
Jantung pesakit lemah.

862
00:59:13,341 --> 00:59:14,759
Budak ini…

863
00:59:14,842 --> 00:59:16,594
Dia menipu. Semuanya tipu!

864
00:59:16,678 --> 00:59:18,137
Bertenang. Orang tak dengar pun.

865
00:59:18,221 --> 00:59:19,472
Saya boleh lawan.

866
00:59:23,142 --> 00:59:24,102
Itu saja.

867
00:59:24,894 --> 00:59:27,313
Pemeriksaan balas, pendakwa.

868
00:59:30,817 --> 00:59:31,901
En. Lee.

869
00:59:32,569 --> 00:59:35,613
Berapa jururawat yang ada
semasa pembedahan itu?

870
00:59:37,991 --> 00:59:38,866
Dua.

871
00:59:38,950 --> 00:59:41,369
Sudahlah. Jangan menipu.

872
00:59:41,869 --> 00:59:44,414
Ada lima orang di dalam.

873
00:59:44,497 --> 00:59:46,666
Dan tiga jururawat.

874
00:59:50,044 --> 00:59:52,714
Selain Kim Mi-yeong dan Choi Ji-a
yang encik laporkan,

875
00:59:54,924 --> 00:59:56,801
Oh Jin-suk pun ada di sana.

876
00:59:57,552 --> 00:59:58,595
Apa?

877
00:59:58,678 --> 00:59:59,762
Oh Jin-suk?

878
01:00:01,472 --> 01:00:04,267
Saya tak kenal dia.

879
01:00:04,350 --> 01:00:06,936
Dia ada dengan encik
di bilik bedah sampai habis.

880
01:00:07,729 --> 01:00:08,855
Bagus, semua.

881
01:00:08,938 --> 01:00:10,940
- Bagus.
- Bagus.

882
01:00:11,024 --> 01:00:13,359
<i>Dia saksi yang nampak semuanya</i>

883
01:00:13,943 --> 01:00:14,944
<i>paling dekat.</i>

884
01:00:18,656 --> 01:00:20,116
Encik dengar?

885
01:00:20,199 --> 01:00:22,368
Encik?

886
01:00:23,536 --> 01:00:25,997
Aduh, apa pula?

887
01:00:26,956 --> 01:00:29,500
Saluran udara tersekat.
Kena buat pembedahan kecemasan!

888
01:00:31,169 --> 01:00:32,795
Kita nak buat trakeostomi?

889
01:00:33,713 --> 01:00:35,340
- Doktor!
- Diam!

890
01:00:35,423 --> 01:00:36,966
Biar saya uruskan, okey?

891
01:00:44,724 --> 01:00:46,893
Encik tak nak jenayah terdedah,

892
01:00:47,685 --> 01:00:48,895
<i>lalu sorok saksi,</i>

893
01:00:49,896 --> 01:00:51,439
<i>Oh Jin-suk, disebabkan takut.</i>

894
01:00:56,152 --> 01:00:57,987
Saya bantah, Yang Arif.

895
01:00:58,988 --> 01:01:00,823
Saya nak dengar dulu.

896
01:01:01,407 --> 01:01:04,118
Pendakwa, tadi awak berikan hujah penting.

897
01:01:04,202 --> 01:01:08,456
Boleh kami dengar keterangan Oh Jin-suk,
yang awak dakwa dia saksi?

898
01:01:10,208 --> 01:01:11,292
Sekarang

899
01:01:11,876 --> 01:01:13,586
tak boleh lagi.

900
01:01:14,879 --> 01:01:19,050
Peguam plaintif nak ubah topik
dengan dakwaan tak berasas.

901
01:01:19,133 --> 01:01:22,345
Sila anggap keterangan dia tak sesuai.

902
01:01:22,428 --> 01:01:23,596
Bantahan diterima.

903
01:01:24,138 --> 01:01:26,099
Pendakwa, jangan berhujah sembarangan.

904
01:01:26,683 --> 01:01:27,642
Ya, Yang Arif.

905
01:01:28,309 --> 01:01:29,435
Jadi hari ini,

906
01:01:30,687 --> 01:01:33,856
saya nak usulkan raut wajah dia saja
sebagai bahan bukti.

907
01:01:34,649 --> 01:01:36,943
Raut wajah tak boleh jadi bahan bukti.

908
01:01:49,539 --> 01:01:50,498
Itu saja.

909
01:02:12,019 --> 01:02:12,854
Defendan.

910
01:02:13,855 --> 01:02:15,440
Kemalangan begini kerap berlaku?

911
01:02:16,190 --> 01:02:18,818
Tak, kes ini jarang berlaku.

912
01:02:18,901 --> 01:02:21,696
Jadi, mesti encik tertanya
punca kemalangan itu.

913
01:02:23,406 --> 01:02:24,490
Sebenarnya…

914
01:02:26,242 --> 01:02:29,078
Kalau susah nak bercakap,
boleh saya bercakap bagi pihak encik?

915
01:02:29,871 --> 01:02:30,872
Boleh.

916
01:02:32,123 --> 01:02:34,625
Sebenarnya, Lee Gang-pung…

917
01:02:36,127 --> 01:02:37,545
gengster.

918
01:02:38,504 --> 01:02:39,881
- Apa?
- Gengster?

919
01:02:39,964 --> 01:02:40,882
Biar betul!

920
01:02:40,965 --> 01:02:42,884
- Betulkah?
- Aduhai.

921
01:02:45,803 --> 01:02:47,221
Dia merepek apa?

922
01:02:47,305 --> 01:02:48,806
Gang-pung pemandu teksi.

923
01:02:50,141 --> 01:02:51,058
Yang Arif.

924
01:02:51,559 --> 01:02:55,062
Peguam bela buat cerita di mahkamah.

925
01:02:55,146 --> 01:02:56,022
Bukan buat cerita.

926
01:02:59,484 --> 01:03:01,944
Lee Gang-pung pernah masuk Geng Oseong

927
01:03:02,028 --> 01:03:03,654
<i>- di Daejeon 20 tahun lepas.</i>
- Tuan!

928
01:03:05,072 --> 01:03:06,449
Pernah disabitkan menyerang.

929
01:03:07,658 --> 01:03:09,494
Sila tengok parut pembedahan dia di sini.

930
01:03:09,577 --> 01:03:11,871
Dadanya pernah ditikam
di bahagian kiri dulu.

931
01:03:12,455 --> 01:03:14,665
Pesakit dengan rekod pembedahan jantung

932
01:03:14,749 --> 01:03:17,126
mati akibat jantung terhenti
semasa pembedahan dia.

933
01:03:17,710 --> 01:03:19,003
Tak pentingkah?

934
01:03:26,344 --> 01:03:27,553
Habislah.

935
01:03:30,014 --> 01:03:31,224
Yang Arif.

936
01:03:31,307 --> 01:03:34,143
Peguam bela menghina si mati

937
01:03:34,227 --> 01:03:36,062
dan menimbulkan kebencian

938
01:03:36,145 --> 01:03:38,940
dengan tunjukkan gambar tak perlu
dan mengungkit kisah silam.

939
01:03:39,023 --> 01:03:40,233
Diterima.

940
01:03:40,316 --> 01:03:42,193
Peguam bela, hati-hati.

941
01:03:42,276 --> 01:03:45,279
Saya takkan ungkit kisah silam dia

942
01:03:45,363 --> 01:03:47,949
kalau kelakuan dia hanya pada masa silam.

943
01:03:48,533 --> 01:03:51,994
Dia masih buat kecoh,
berkasar dan tak beri kerjasama

944
01:03:52,078 --> 01:03:54,121
semasa dia di hospital.

945
01:03:54,789 --> 01:03:55,790
Dia menipu.

946
01:03:55,873 --> 01:03:58,876
Sila jelaskan kelakuan dia di hospital.

947
01:03:59,836 --> 01:04:01,003
Pesakit Lee Gang-pung…

948
01:04:05,299 --> 01:04:06,676
sentiasa mencarut.

949
01:04:07,802 --> 01:04:10,555
Dia selalu takutkan jururawat
dengan perangai bengisnya.

950
01:04:11,222 --> 01:04:14,225
Saya dengar
keluarga dia pun dilayan begitu.

951
01:04:18,980 --> 01:04:19,897
Tak.

952
01:04:23,609 --> 01:04:24,527
Itu tak betul.

953
01:04:32,285 --> 01:04:34,620
Takkan jadi di sini?

954
01:04:34,704 --> 01:04:35,997
Ada satu lagi.

955
01:04:36,998 --> 01:04:38,875
Saya dengar dia dera anak perempuannya.

956
01:04:39,709 --> 01:04:43,004
Sampai anak dia dapat anoreksia
dan berkurung di dalam bilik.

957
01:04:43,796 --> 01:04:45,256
<i>Orang dirasuk</i>

958
01:04:45,339 --> 01:04:48,217
<i>apabila keinginan mereka memuncak.</i>

959
01:04:48,885 --> 01:04:50,887
Apabila jumpa orang yang dibenci,

960
01:04:50,970 --> 01:04:53,014
atau sesuatu yang timbulkan kemarahan,

961
01:04:53,806 --> 01:04:56,225
kemungkinan untuk dirasuk meningkat.

962
01:04:57,476 --> 01:04:58,477
Hei, kau.

963
01:04:59,061 --> 01:05:01,480
Kau dah gila?

964
01:05:02,064 --> 01:05:05,610
Kau cakap ikut sedap mulut
sebab kau tak nampak apa-apa, bukan?

965
01:05:06,152 --> 01:05:07,737
Apa guna mata itu?

966
01:05:07,820 --> 01:05:10,406
Kalau tak nak, beri aku.

967
01:05:11,032 --> 01:05:14,785
Aduh, teringat zaman dulu.

968
01:05:15,328 --> 01:05:16,996
Dulu kerap juga aku keluar masuk

969
01:05:17,079 --> 01:05:18,247
penjara.

970
01:05:18,331 --> 01:05:21,959
Dia merepek apa? Kenapa dengan pipi dia?

971
01:05:22,043 --> 01:05:24,045
Mak, saya rasa

972
01:05:24,128 --> 01:05:25,463
tak sedap hati pula.

973
01:05:26,839 --> 01:05:29,175
Pendakwa, sila balik ke meja awak.

974
01:05:29,258 --> 01:05:31,218
Kenapa aku pula kena duduk?

975
01:05:31,302 --> 01:05:33,346
Lelaki itu yang patut duduk

976
01:05:33,429 --> 01:05:34,430
di dalam keranda dia.

977
01:05:34,513 --> 01:05:39,602
Berani kau buat kacau
dengan tipu semua orang?

978
01:05:39,685 --> 01:05:42,104
Mulut kau memang nak kena ajar. Mari sini…

979
01:06:30,194 --> 01:06:31,654
Bencinya jadi

980
01:06:33,114 --> 01:06:34,699
peguam yang boleh nampak hantu.

981
01:07:07,773 --> 01:07:09,525
{\an8}Semuanya jadi begini sebab saya lembik.

982
01:07:09,608 --> 01:07:11,527
{\an8}<i>Tak! Bukan sekarang!</i>

983
01:07:11,610 --> 01:07:13,821
{\an8}Jangan kacau kalau kau sayang nyawa.

984
01:07:13,904 --> 01:07:15,614
{\an8}<i>Mereka usulkan rekod palsu.</i>

985
01:07:15,698 --> 01:07:16,741
{\an8}<i>Semak rekod perubatan.</i>

986
01:07:16,824 --> 01:07:19,452
{\an8}<i>Kira bertuahlah Peguam Han bela awak.</i>

987
01:07:19,535 --> 01:07:21,620
{\an8}Na-hyun sanggup
gadai nyawa demi perbicaraan.

988
01:07:21,704 --> 01:07:23,205
{\an8}<i>Saya dari Pejabat Pendakwa.</i>

989
01:07:23,289 --> 01:07:25,166
{\an8}Peduli apa dia pendakwa. Tangkap dia.

990
01:07:30,046 --> 01:07:31,422
{\an8}- Siapa kau?
- Aku?

991
01:07:34,008 --> 01:07:36,844
{\an8}<i>Aku peguam gengster, Lee Gang-pung!</i>

992
01:07:38,095 --> 01:07:42,767
{\an8}Terjemahan sari kata oleh Aizat Bahri

